imos
Class Act

java.lang.Object
  imos.Act
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAct, java.lang.Comparable<IAct>
public class Act
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAct

An act is the association of a schema with the feedback the agent receives when trying to enact that schema. The term Act and the term interaction are used indifferently.

Author:
mcohen, ogeorgeon
